sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Jupyter as JupyterLab Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant Kernel as Jupyter Kernel<br/>Internal IPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PyPI as PyPI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3

    Note over User,Kernel: Flow 1: User Access to Jupyter Workbench
    User->>Router: HTTPS Request<br/>GET /lab<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS 8443<br/>OpenShift Session
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift Token<br/>Check namespace access
    OAuth->>Jupyter: Authenticated Request<br/>HTTP 8888
    Jupyter->>Kernel: Execute Code<br/>IPC (Local Process)
    Kernel-->>Jupyter: Execution Results
    Jupyter-->>OAuth: HTML/JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Jupyter,S3: Flow 2: Workbench to S3 Storage
    Jupyter->>S3: Upload Training Data<br/>PUT /bucket/data.csv<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM Credentials
    S3-->>Jupyter: Upload Complete<br/>200 OK
    Jupyter->>S3: Download Model<br/>GET /bucket/model.pkl<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>AWS IAM Credentials
    S3-->>Jupyter: Model Artifacts

    Note over Jupyter,PyPI: Python Package Installation
    User->>Jupyter: pip install scikit-learn
    Jupyter->>PyPI: GET /simple/scikit-learn<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    PyPI-->>Jupyter: Package Index
    Jupyter->>PyPI: GET /packages/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    PyPI-->>Jupyter: Package Files
    Jupyter->>Jupyter: Install Package
    Jupyter-->>User: Installation Complete

    Note over Jupyter,GitHub: Git Operations
    User->>Jupyter: git clone repo
    Jupyter->>GitHub: HTTPS/443 or SSH/22<br/>Git Credentials/SSH Key
    GitHub-->>Jupyter: Repository Contents
    User->>Jupyter: git push
    Jupyter->>GitHub: HTTPS/443<br/>Git Token Auth
    GitHub-->>Jupyter: Push Accepted

    Note over Jupyter,K8sAPI: Kubernetes CLI Operations
    User->>Jupyter: oc get pods
    Jupyter->>K8sAPI: GET /api/v1/namespaces/.../pods<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.3<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Jupyter: Pod List JSON
    Jupyter-->>User: Display Pods

    Note over User,Jupyter: WebSocket Connection (Jupyter Kernels)
    User->>Router: WebSocket Upgrade<br/>WSS Connection
    Router->>OAuth: Forward WebSocket
    OAuth->>Jupyter: WebSocket to Kernel Gateway<br/>WS/8888
    Jupyter->>Kernel: Execute Cell<br/>IPC
    Kernel-->>Jupyter: Stream Output
    Jupyter-->>OAuth: WebSocket Messages
    OAuth-->>Router: Forward Messages
    Router-->>User: Live Output Stream
